1. *Crveni* voz vozi preko železničke pruge. (The red train is running over the railway.)

2. Ona je nosila *crvenu* haljinu. (She was wearing a red dress.)

3. *Crvenilo* je obasjalo njenu licu. (Her face was flushed.)

4. Oni su se igrali u *crvenom* parku. (They were playing in the red park.)

5. Ona je mazila *crvenu* boju na zid. (She was painting the wall red.)